Gorgeous two story on a large corner lot in sought after Redmond Ridge.This home has been exceptionally well maintained and features a formal living & dining room, office/den, huge loft, and 4 bed 2.5 bath including a primary suite w/5-piece bath & large walk-in closet. The kitchen is a cook's dream brand new w/quartz counters, stainless appliances, gas range, and large island. Enjoy gatherings in the generously sized family room with gas fireplace.Oversized 2-car garage. This absolutely stunning home comes w/brand new carpet & fresh interior paint. Highly rated Rosa Parks Elem, Timberline Middle, mins to downtown Redmond, freeway, trails & parks.

2 homes on 5 secluded private acres with Mtn Views. Stick built 3 bed/2.25 baths, open concept & vaulted ceilings, wood stove w/custom door, tons of natural light, king sized primary suite, 2 double sized closets, custom lighting and bathroom w/Bluetooth, large bedrooms w/ big closets, newly remodeled country kitchen, granite counters, custom lights, stainless appls & tons of storage. RV Parking, circle drive, new gravel & all fenced, large pasture below home, amazing outdoor living space, BBQ platform w/ professional grill, Edison lights, 4 sheds, large work shop and chicken coop. New well pump, water heater, engineered hardwood floors, lighting and paint.  2015 Single wide on own septic, shed, 2 bed/1 bath, large kitchen and living room.

Bright, modern 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhouse in fantastic Wildwood community! Rare end unit for extra  privacy. Large living room w/ open floor plan, shiny floors, lots of windows, cozy fireplace, balcony. Sunny kitchen w/ granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, island, modern white cabinets, adjacent dining area. All-new flooring & light fixtures & blinds. Spacious upstairs master bedroom w/ en-suite bathroom. Nice-sized 2nd bed room & additional full-sized bathroom down the hall. Third room and bath on ground floor, perfect for office or guest room. Attached single-car garage + assigned parking spot. Community amenities include gym, pool, & hot tub. Excellent location near freeways, shopping, & restaurants. Ready for move-in!

Impeccably remodeled home in Juanita. Great room on the main level, with big windows on three walls. New chef’s kitchen with custom-built cabinetry, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. New front door, interior doors, and vinyl double-pane windows. New flooring throughout. Magnificent owner’s suite, with sumptuous en suite bathroom and huge closet. Lower level features double-size rec room; easy to divide into two rooms. Incredible outdoor entertaining spaces, including decks on both levels of the home. Flat, sunny backyard with big lawn and garden space. Parking pad for boats and RVs. Unbeatable location, within strolling distance of Juanita Beach Park and The Village at Totem Lake. Presented in absolute turn-key condition.

A rare find! Beautiful custom built home on 1.86+acres in East Olympia. This stunning, move-in ready 4BD 2.75BA home has been meticulously well-maintained inside & out and offers plenty of space & privacy. Main level features a marble entryway, a Den or 4th bedroom, formal living w/ cathedral ceiling, formal dining room, family room, bathroom with shower & utility room. Gourmet kitchen comes with a huge island perfect for entertaining, granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. Upstairs you will find the bright and spacious master suite with a gorgeous 5pc master bath, 2 more good sized bedrooms & another full bath. Private patio and beautiful landscaping. Attached 3 car garage. Add'l shed/garage perfect for storage. Pre-inspected!

address: 34100 Mountain Loop Hwy, Granite Falls, WA 98252

Also includes electric wall heat. 2 Car Detached Carport, Private Well w/Pump House and extra storage. On Septic & Well so only utility would be Electric. address: 231 Belmont Ave E UNIT 209, Seattle, WA 98102

Secure building with garage parking and storage included. Walk score of 98 Transit score of 82. Bike score of 78. Urban living at its best.

Great investment rental on the  South Hill.? Check out this 2 bedroom/1 bath home with so much character. Don’t miss your chance.

address: 22 Country Club Dr SW APT C, Lakewood, WA 98498
Description: The iconic Tacoma Country & Golf Club is situated on the shores of American Lake and is home to this luxury waterfront condo w/ the Golf Course right out your door.  A unique lifestyle, luxury living, sophisticated main level living w/ lower level attached garage, open-concept, lake views, western-facing & dock. Main level living w/ Owners suite with 5-piece attached bath, soak tub, walk-in shower & huge walk-in closet. Updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Lower level high end garage w/ epoxy and TV along with abundant storage. Full facility private Country Club 18 hole championship Golf Course, 50 meter pool, tennis court, gym, spa, and the clubhouse with dining, lounge and full menu of activities.  5 Member HOA includes dock.

MLS# 253390 River Walk Village invites you to live everyday like it is a holiday on the shores of the Columbia River! This spacious 2 story condo is perfect for low maintenance living with memorable views from the private patio, balcony, and most windows. The main level has an open floor plan with hardwood floors throughout, with a living room with welcoming fireplace, and a kitchen with stainless steel appliances, large breakfast bar, wood cabinetry, granite counter-tops, full tile backsplash, pantry, and spacious dining area. 2 of the 4 bedrooms are master suits, one on each floor, with a fabulous river view, direct access to the patio or balcony, walk-in closets, dual sinks, tubs and tiled showers. The lower-level master suite includes a jetted tub and heated floors and towel rack. A spacious laundry room and ½ bath are discreetly located on the first floor. The second floor consists of a large open family room with surround sound, wet bar, and access to the balcony. Off the family room is set of double doors opening into spacious bedroom/office/gym. This room is designed to easily be customized to your taste. With all this living space, 3310SF, 4 rooms, 3.5 baths, 2 car garage you’ll be able to easily adapt to a changing life style whether its family, entertaining, working from home, or leisure. Come enjoy the miles of river  paths, parks, golf, marina, shopping, restaurants, and entertainment all within short distance. Commuters will like the easy access to interstate and 15 minute drive to the airport.

Plenty of room with this 4 bedroom rambler on 2.7 acres in the country. Peek a boo mountain view from front of home. Updated light and open kitchen w/beautiful granite counters, updated stainless steel appliances, custom soft close cupboards. Huge primary bedroom w/walk in closet & en suite full bath including whirlpool tub. Split bedroom floor plan, full main bath, bonus room off kitchen w/extra finished room that would work well for office/craft space, and half bath. Additional large, finished room with additional entrance from front deck could be used as 5th bedroom (4 bedroom septic). Detached garage wired for 220 includes shop with separate entrance and space for storage/office. Close to Hwy 7 for commutes, quick 10 min drive to town.
